<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="BestLowCostRentals.com affiliate disclosure — how we earn from links on this site.">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-navy mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <p>BestLowCostRentals.com is a free comparison service. We earn a commission when you book through some of the links on this site. This commission comes from the rental company or booking platform — not from you. You pay the same price whether you use our link or book directly.</p>
    <p>Our affiliate partners include Discover Cars, Booking.com, Rentalcars.com, Travelpayouts, and VIP Cars. When we include widgets or comparison tools from these platforms, they may track your visit using cookies. You can opt out of tracking by using your browser's private/incognito mode.</p>
    <p>We also generate income from lead generation — when you submit a quote request through our form, we may share your details with verified Dubai rental companies who may contact you with quotes. We do not sell your data to third parties outside of this rental context.</p>
    <p>Our editorial content — guides, comparisons, and recommendations — is independent of our commercial relationships. We do not accept payment to rank or recommend specific companies in our articles. Our recommendations reflect our genuine assessment of value and service quality.</p>
    <p>If you have questions about our disclosure, contact us at hello@bestlowcostrentals.com.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
